         <abstract>
            <p>In this paper we discuss three topics on the designing of the limiter functions. (1) To guarantee the TVD property (2) To maintain enough artificial viscosity. (3) A method to form TVB limiter which can ensure second order accuracy even at the extrema of the solution.</p>
